on your psychological profile.

38:21.175 --> 38:23.803
<i>"Introduction to First Year Adult Psychology."</i>

38:23.886 --> 38:26.973
I haven't read the whole thing,
but I read from page eight to...

38:27.056 --> 38:29.141
Well, I've read most of page eight.

38:29.225 --> 38:30.810
And here's what happened to you.

38:30.893 --> 38:32.645
A long, long time ago,

38:32.728 --> 38:34.522
