40:21.504 --> 40:23.589
I embarrassed the whole
team this morning and I'm sorry.

40:23.672 --> 40:25.174
It won't happen again.

40:26.509 --> 40:27.676
I love you, Will.

40:28.886 --> 40:30.387
Thanks, sis.

