41:01.544 --> 41:03.045
It's a good game.

41:05.756 --> 41:07.341
- Jerry Dantana?
- Yes, sir.

41:07.424 --> 41:09.593
This is Maggie Jordan.
She's also a producer on the story.

41:09.677 --> 41:11.095
