41:11.178 --> 41:12.638
No, she's a producer on the story.

41:12.721 --> 41:15.766
- She understands...
- I was told Jerry Dantana.

41:16.100 --> 41:17.184
Sir...

41:17.268 --> 41:20.521
Charlie Skinner
and MacKenzie McHale told me Jerry Dantana,

41:20.604 --> 41:23.774
